Dobrescu +0302.22h4h2 (1976). Version

Date: September 8, 2025

File: Dobrescu1976a.pgn

In the sideline of the correction, after 4. Kh5 Kxg2 Black loses, whereas the better 4 Rc5+ leads to the mainline. Due to the Rc5+ resource the original study is correct. The version takes advantage of this and extends the study by one move.
